Bartered Gold is and expirimental electronic duo from Riverside, 
California. They produce downtempo, glitch, electro, and chiptunes. The album Fighter Pilot is a five-track EP released at no cost on Bandcamp, Soundcloud, and The Pirate Bay. It is the second album in the Bartered Gold discography. The albums can be found (and purchased) at [see .nfo]
